article_title: Conservatives take notice of Sen. Jerry Moran’s vote with Sen. Ted Cruz on omnibus spending bill
article_text: Jerry Moran of Kansas was one of only 11 Republican senators who teamed up this month with tea party favorite Ted Cruz on three votes intended to stall or defeat the $1.1 trillion omnibus spending bill – a failed but headline-grabbing maneuver that put him at odds with GOP leadership.
